{"tid":699158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特金會】簽成協議激親習帝？中國媒體冷處理 微博禁評論","createTime":"2018-06-12T09:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T09:38:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"01989d9bdc62127b0bbc831a322489965dc5633b","tid":699158,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180612/large/1528783695_9a47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180612%2Flarge%2F1528783695_9a47.jpg&h=5df3751d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180612/large/1528784243_96a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180612%2Flarge%2F1528784243_96a4.jpg&h=d0ebd966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n備受矚目的「特金會」進展順利，美國總統特朗普和北韓最高領導人金正恩在會晤後簽署文件。不過，內地媒體卻一反之4小時前對「特金世紀一握」的熱情處理，以冷淡態度對待，微博更是禁止了評論。<br />\n<br />\n美國《華爾街日報》中文網率先在其官方微博以快訊的方式，發佈特朗普與金正恩簽署重要文件的消息，並指「金正恩稱，將過去拋開，世界將見證巨大變化。特朗普稱，與金正恩簽署相當全面的文件，包括很多工作。」但隨即被微博禁止評論，唯一一名發表了評論的網友，也已被刪帖。<br />\n<br />\n中國的媒體沒有搶着發佈有關消息，只有中共喉舌《環球時報》與官媒央視報道，《環時》微博發出的同時，禁止評論，而央視的微博則選擇性地留下網友評留，而獲准留下的評論，都是針對特朗普與金正恩坐姿的，與協議無關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180612/58308332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180612%2F58308332&d=ZzA5IRrzd3BZ%2FN4D7BApPTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=918c5747\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180612%2F58308332&h=f7f76c30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180612/58308332</a>"}]}